metadata.name: Lethe
metadata.description:
Lethe, the incarnate of the "river of oblivion", where we are both ourselves and where we lose ourselves, will guide us on our endless journey. When we will take just a sip of the river’s water, this magnanimous spirit will grant us a mind of a newborn and wash away all the pains of our mortal lives.
